query.query: {"measures":[["count","*"]],"groups":[["ActivityDate_Year","ActivityDate_Week"]],"filters":[["IsClosed",["true"],"in"]]}

{"measures":[["sum","amount"]],"pigql":"a = load \"opportunity\"; b = filter a by 'IsWon' == \"true\" || 'IsClosed' == \"false\"; b = group b by all; b = foreach b generate \"Forecast\" as 'Group', coalesce(sum('Amount'), 0) as 'sum_amount'; c = filter a by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate \"Won\" as 'Group', coalesce(sum('Amount'), 0) as 'sum_amount'; d = group a by all; d = foreach d generate coalesce({{cell(kpi_quota_forecast_hidden.result, 0, \"sum_QuotaAmount\").asString()}}, 0) as 'sum_amount', \"Quota\" as 'Group'; e = union c, b, d;","groups":["Group"]}

{"measures":[["sum","percent"]],"pigql":"opp_history = load \"pipeline_trending\"; opp_history = filter opp_history by 'Stage.IsClosed' == \"false\"; today = filter opp_history by date('ValidFromDate_Year', 'ValidFromDate_Month', 'ValidFromDate_Day') in [..\"current day\"]; today = filter today by date('ValidToDate_Year', 'ValidToDate_Month', 'ValidToDate_Day') in [\"1 day ahead\"..]; today = foreach today generate coalesce(sum('Amount'), 0) as 'Amount'; last_week = filter opp_history by date('ValidFromDate_Year', 'ValidFromDate_Month', 'ValidFromDate_Day') in [..\"8 day ago\"]; last_week = filter last_week by date('ValidToDate_Year', 'ValidToDate_Month', 'ValidToDate_Day') in [\"7 days ago\"..]; last_week = foreach last_week generate coalesce(sum('Amount'), 0) as 'AmountP'; s = group today by all full, last_week by all; s = foreach s generate (case when coalesce(sum(last_week['AmountP']), 0) == 0 && coalesce(sum(today['Amount']), 0) > 0 then 1.0 else coalesce((coalesce(sum(today['Amount']), 0) - coalesce(sum(last_week['AmountP']), 0)) / coalesce(sum(last_week['AmountP']), 0), 0) end) as 'sum_percent';"}

{"measures":[["sum","percent"]],"pigql":"opp = load \"opportunity\"; opp = filter opp by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; today = filter opp by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [..\"current day\"]; last_week = filter opp by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [..\"7 days ago\"]; s = group today by all full, last_week by all; s = foreach s generate (case when coalesce(sum(last_week['Amount']), 0) == 0 && coalesce(sum(today['Amount']), 0) > 0 then 1.0 else coalesce((coalesce(sum(today['Amount']), 0) - coalesce(sum(last_week['Amount']), 0)) / coalesce(sum(last_week['Amount']), 0), 0) end) as 'sum_percent';"}

{"measures":[["sum","percent","color"]],"pigql":"q = load \"opportunity\"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate {{coalesce(cell(kpi_activities_completed_comparision.result, 0, \"sum_percent\"), 0).asObject()}} as 'sum_percent'; q = foreach q generate (case when 'sum_percent' > 0 then \"#0BA976\" when 'sum_percent' < 0 then \"#C03757\" else \"#44517D\" end) as 'color', 'sum_percent' as 'sum_percent';","autoFilter":false}

{"measures":[["sum","percent"]],"pigql":"team_opptys = load \"opportunity\"; team_opptys = filter team_opptys by {{column(dropdown_parent_id_hidden.result, [\"Role.DeveloperName\"]).asEquality(\"Owner.Role.DeveloperName\")}}; team_opptys = filter team_opptys by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; team_opptys = group team_opptys by 'Owner.UniqueUserName'; team_opptys = foreach team_opptys generate 'Owner.UniqueUserName' as 'Owner.UniqueUserName', coalesce(sum('Amount'), 0) as 'owner_amount'; team_opptys = group team_opptys by all; team_opptys = foreach team_opptys generate coalesce(coalesce(sum('owner_amount'), 0) / unique('Owner.UniqueUserName'), 0) as 'team_avg'; team_opptys = foreach team_opptys generate coalesce(({{coalesce(cell(kpi_closed_won.result, 0, \"sum_Amount\"), 0).asObject()}} - coalesce(sum('team_avg'), 0)) / coalesce(sum('team_avg'), 0), 0) as 'sum_percent';"}
{"measures":[["sum","Amount"]],"groups":[["CloseDate_Year","CloseDate_Week"]],"filters":[["IsWon",["true"],"in"]]}

{"measures":[["sum","percent"]],"pigql":"team_opptys = load \"opportunity\"; team_opptys = filter team_opptys by {{column(dropdown_parent_id_hidden.result, [\"Role.DeveloperName\"]).asEquality(\"Owner.Role.DeveloperName\")}}; team_opptys = filter team_opptys by 'IsClosed' == \"false\"; team_opptys = group team_opptys by 'Owner.UniqueUserName'; team_opptys = foreach team_opptys generate 'Owner.UniqueUserName' as 'Owner.UniqueUserName', coalesce(sum('Amount'), 0) as 'owner_amount'; team_opptys = group team_opptys by all; team_opptys = foreach team_opptys generate coalesce(coalesce(sum('owner_amount'), 0) / unique('Owner.UniqueUserName'), 0) as 'team_avg'; team_opptys = foreach team_opptys generate coalesce(({{coalesce(cell(kpi_open_pipe.result, 0, \"sum_Amount\"), 0).asObject()}} - coalesce(sum('team_avg'), 0)) / coalesce(sum('team_avg'), 0), 0) as 'sum_percent';"}

kpi_remaining_after_forecast.query: a = load "opportunity"; a = group a by all; b = foreach a generate (case when {{coalesce(cell(kpi_quota_forecast_hidden.result, 0, "sum_QuotaAmount"), 0).asObject()}} - sum('Amount') > 0 then {{coalesce(cell(kpi_quota_forecast_hidden.result, 0, "sum_QuotaAmount"), 0).asObject()}} - sum('Amount') else 0 end) as 'sum_QuotaAmount';

kpi_quota_remaining_to_close.query: won = load "opportunity"; won = filter won by 'IsWon' == "true"; won = foreach won generate coalesce(sum('Amount'), 0) as 'sum_Amount'; quota = load "quota"; quota = group quota by all; quota = foreach quota generate coalesce(sum('QuotaAmount'), 0) as 'sum_quota'; remain = group won by all full, quota by all; remain = foreach remain generate coalesce(sum(quota['sum_quota']), 0) - coalesce(sum(won['sum_Amount']), 0) as 'sum_quota_remaining'; remain = foreach remain generate (case when sum('sum_quota_remaining') > 0 then sum('sum_quota_remaining') else 0 end) as 'sum_quota_remaining';

query.query: {"measures":[["sum","AnnualRevenue"]],"limit":10,"groups":["Name"],"filters":[["hasOpportunity",["false"],"in"]],"order":[[-1,{"ascending":false}]]}

kpi_quota_attainment.query: won = load "opportunity"; won = filter won by 'IsWon' == "true"; q = load "quota"; attainment = group won by all full, q by all; attainment = foreach attainment generate (case when sum(won['Amount']) / sum(q['QuotaAmount']) > 0 then sum(won['Amount']) / sum(q['QuotaAmount']) else 0 end) as 'sum_quota_attainment';

kpi_pipe_coverage.query: won = load "opportunity"; won = filter won by 'IsWon' == "true"; quota = load "quota"; quota_remaining = group won by all full, quota by all; quota_remaining = foreach quota_remaining generate sum(quota['QuotaAmount']) as 'quota', coalesce(sum(won['Amount']), 0) as 'amount'; quota_remaining = foreach quota_remaining generate (case when sum('quota') - sum('amount') > 0 then sum('quota') - sum('amount') else 0 end) as 'quota_remaining'; open = load "opportunity"; open = filter open by 'IsClosed' == "false"; coverage = group quota_remaining by all full, open by all; coverage = foreach coverage generate coalesce(sum(open['Amount']), 0) as 'amount', sum(quota_remaining['quota_remaining']) as 'quota_remaining'; coverage = foreach coverage generate round(coalesce(sum('amount') / sum('quota_remaining'), 0), 1) as 'sum_pipe_coverage'; f = filter coverage by 'sum_pipe_coverage' > 0;
